snippet.title: Let's Reach for the Stars EI
snippet.description:
We're reaching for the stars in this let's play of a very unknown 4X space game. It's unfortunately incomplete due to the producer going bankrupt. It's a good game design-wise though, I like how they kept it simple.

Edit: It appears the 'End turn' sound in this game was used in the K-On anime, ep. 1. That's... interesting. Or maybe coincidence that it sounds so similar.
